From 0dff22a6174fa62caf70dae7730fcbf992e403e8 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Sean <sean@calculusholdings.com>
Date: Sat, 28 Feb 2026 23:05:05 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: 8-agent flow controllers, Day 1 audit fixes, 91/91
 tests green

- Add 8 model-specific flow controllers (DMC, CT, TILT, Mortgage,
  Real Estate, Eureka, Loan Servicing, IFSE) with phase-based
  state machines, auth tiers, tool routing, and system prompts
- Extend CalcModel enum to 8 values (add MORTGAGE, REAL_ESTATE,
  LOAN_SERVICING) across types, DB schema, and phone mapping
- Add env-driven PHONE_MODEL_MAP for all 8 inbound numbers
- Add startup env validation (fatal vs warning severity)
- Fix fuzzy opt-out regex to handle natural language variations
- Fix 8 test failures: align e2e tests with refactored compliance
  enforcer API (CallContext, GateCheckResult[], detectPII, scorecard)
- Add @types/pg to devDependencies
- 0 TypeScript errors, 91/91 tests passing

Files: 35 src + 3 tests = 13,200 lines
